
# <type>(<scope>): <subject>   ── 50 chars max ─────────────────|
#
# <body>   ── wrap at 72 ───────────────────────────────────────────────|
#
# <footer>
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Type:    feat | fix | refactor | docs | test | chore | perf | build | ci
# Scope:   the area touched (optional). e.g. auth, api, ui
# Subject: imperative, present tense. "add x" not "added x" or "adds x"
#
# Body:    why, not what. The diff already shows what changed.
# Footer:  BREAKING CHANGE: ... or  Closes #123, Refs #456
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
